      "span_text": "This is due to the simplicity of RF-WPT that neither large coils (with diameter of 0.6m in [CITATION_3] nor scrupulous resonance alignment is needed. Most importantly, RF-WPT brings about the minimal cost increase, because it can be implemented by adding several basic electronic elements such as rectifier, capacitors and diodes to the existing circuits [CITATION_4] )."
